          tutorials are below.
          If you have any comments or questions, please contact us via our <a href = "/contact">contact
          form</a> or at <% include ./partials/mailto %></p>
        <h3>Planned Tutorials</h3>
        <div id="accordion" style="text-align: left;">
          <h3>Introduction</h3>
          <div>
            <p>
            Coming soon!
            </p>
          </div>
          <h3>Basic Electronics</h3>
          <div>
            <p>
